  "analysis": "The autotune background process (PID 2918) is running and has read the parquet files and created the fastText-format files. No valid `/app/model.bin` exists yet. Autotune is configured for ~900 seconds with a 150MB model size constraint, so we need to continue polling the log, process status, and model files until it completes. The stale large model files from the previous failed runs were removed.",
